de.espirit.firstspirit.webedit.plugin.inlineedit.InlineEditContext

  • Packages that use InlineEditContext 
    Package Description
    de.espirit.firstspirit.webedit.plugin.inlineedit
    Provides interfaces and types for web client inline edit plugins.

    This package provides types, interfaces and classes, that are to be used to integrate web client plugins via the public hotspot of FirstSpirit into the inline edit area of the web client.
